Who We Are - BSW Wealth Partners: Colorado's Leading Wealth Advisory Firm

































































































 











 





 




















  


















				Who:			





We Make Life Better for people just like you: successful individuals and families who want to focus on their passions and delegate the business of their life to us. 


Contact Us

BSW Team CultureProfessional PartnersHistory











  















				BSW Team Culture			







BSW is: Independent, Employee-owned, Woman-founded, and Built To Last.





BSW Wealth Partners is a multi-family office and wealth advisory firm serving a national and international clientele from offices in Boulder and Denver. Named by the Financial Times as one of nation’s top 300 advisory firms, we provide best-in-class advisory and investment services with white-glove client care. 
Our commitment to Make Life Better is evident in our own philanthropic efforts. With deep roots in Colorado, BSW gives back to our community both as a firm and as individuals. We support local non-profit organizations and provide paid time off for volunteer work.














  










				Our Team			







Interested in joining our team? Visit Our Careers Page










  















 










				History			





				Since our founding in 1992, BSW has evolved and grown in many capacities. On the cusp of our silver anniversary, we have diligently charted a course for BSW’s next 25 years. Our goal is to be an exceptional and enduring firm.  To us, an exceptional firm provides best-in-class advice, outstanding investment outcomes, personalized and personable service, and the myriad intangibles that enhance your quality of life and peace of mind.  Likewise, an enduring firm is one that is built-to-last, independent, unbiased and capable of serving your family for generations.			








