Nicole Zelyez - BSW Wealth Partners: Colorado's Leading Wealth Advisory Firm


































































































 











 





 











Nicole ZelyezOutreach and Engagement CoordinatorHome » Team » Nicole Zelyez














Nicole Zelyez joined BSW Wealth Partners in 2015 as the Outreach and Engagement Coordinator.  Nicole’s primary role is executing marketing efforts including communication and business development.

Prior to joining the firm, Nicole worked with a private family office in New York City and supported the launch of Retro Report, a non-profit news journalism organization.  Born and raised in New York, Nicole earned her BA in History from Stony Brook University.  When the opportunity to move to Colorado presented itself, Nicole did not think twice and she headed west with her husband and a fluffy black cat.
When away from BSW, Nicole enjoys foraging for wildflowers and herbs or practicing alpine sports including skiing, rock climbing, and ice climbing (as long as it’s not too cold out!).








