Outside of the office, Yiwen enjoys basketball, football, snowboarding, and golfing. A self-professed techie, he also enjoys building, upgrading, integrating, and fixing computers and other systems. Had he not studied business in college, he would have explored astrophysics and other galactic objects, his childhood fascination.
