Eric Davis (CRD# 6065115) 
Eric is an Advisor at BSW Wealth Partners where he supports both the advisory team and the investment group through diligent analysis and dedicated service to clients.
 
Prior to joining BSW, he worked as a financial analyst with investment firm, Janus Capital Group and also spent time as an investment banking analyst with Petrie Partners, an oil and gas focused investment bank. Eric then spent a year in southern Spain fulfilling his entrepreneurial itch by starting a craft-beer brewery. 
 
Eric competed for the University of Colorado NCAA ski team and spends most of his time outside the office skiing. Although he thoroughly enjoys speeding downhill on the slopes, his current fascination is finding powder in the backcountry. He also enjoys climbing, mountain biking, traveling and spending time with family.
 
